    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Short. casual, dark comady story game based in a fictional gray world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You go to school and make your way through the day while trying to survive. You may be bullied, insulted, bruised, and cut but at least your alive right? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's like a visual novel but with walking to make you feel more alone!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game only has one available language, which is English.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Come down the rabbit hole of depression, exploring a boring color scape as you try to make sense of the world in one day. This game uses primarily four to five colors to give off that extra sense of dread. Where better to go than school!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189150/extras/c8f1d6f588af680dc8d37adc7a6e1477.apng?t=1731217916\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189150/extras/c8f1d6f588af680dc8d37adc7a6e1477.poster.avif?t=1731217916\" class=\"bb_img\" width=106 height=106 /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Missing the bus here is no big deal you can walk. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But remember it's just a game!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >About 15 minutes in length for a play through. There're 6 different endings, 8 collectibles, and some mini games. Side content such as small event. and funny quotes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Over 100+ different quotes to find throughout.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unfortunatly there is no controller support as of this version.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3189150/extras/44c4510640340bd0a3d0ed3c8de4e1f6.avif?t=1731217916\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p>",
